-- Madison Square Garden Nears Purchase of Forum, Ex-Los Angeles Lakers Home
-- B y   A n d y   F i x m e r
-- 2010-12-10T19:41:33Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-10/madison-square-garden-nears-purchase-of-forum-ex-los-angeles-lakers-home.html
Madison Square Garden Inc., owner of
the New York Knicks, acquired an option to purchase the Forum,
former home of the Los Angeles Lakers, in Inglewood, California.  The transaction is subject to due diligence and other
conditions, MSG spokeswoman Alysia Lew said today in an e-mail.
She declined to discuss details.  The agreement was reported earlier by Billboard and the Los
Angeles Times.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Andrew Fixmer in Los Angeles at 
